word_mean_info__list.difference: 口语用词，指买卖双方经过交涉达成协议成交。
普通用词，含义广。既可指某种具体的商业又可指广泛的贸易。
多指买卖双方通过谈判、协商就商品质量、数量、价格等项达成协议所成的生意。
多指大规模的买卖或易货关系。
指包括售货、购货、换货在内的综合商业活动，方式可以是批发或零售。

bilingual.source: The city is a nexus of culture and commerce.
bilingual.target: 这座城市是文化和商业的联系。

bilingual.source: The prosperity of industry and commerce has boosted local employment.
bilingual.target: 工商业的繁荣带动了当地的就业。

bilingual.source: The government introduced new policies to promote industry and commerce.
bilingual.target: 政府出台了新的政策来促进工商业的发展。

bilingual.source: They drew up plans aimed at expanding commerce.
bilingual.target: 他们拟定了发展商业的计划。

bilingual.source: They imagined a world without merchants and therefore without commerce.
bilingual.target: 他们幻想了一个没有商人从而也没有商业的世界。

bilingual.source: One test governs state legislation that discriminates against interstate commerce.
bilingual.target: 一个检验约束歧视州际商业的州立法.

bilingual.source: The letter of credit is taken as the lifeline of international commerce.
bilingual.target: 信用证交易被视为国际商业的生命线。

bilingual.source: Our society is still governed mainly by the demands of industry and commerce.
bilingual.target: 我们的社会仍然被工业和商业的需求所主导着。

bilingual.source: The emergence of this project takes the lead in promoting the value of circumjacent commerce.
bilingual.target: 本案推出后,率先带动提升了周边商业的价值.

bilingual.source: Because e-commerce model significantly lower than the traditional business model to save time!
bilingual.target: 因为电子商务模式明显比传统的商业的模式节省时间！

yingyinNormal.en: Uh, just one other matter. I want to talk about taxation of Internet commerce.
yingyinNormal.zh: 还有一件事，我想谈谈互联网商务的税收问题。

yingyinNormal.en: Permit. Receipt of declared commerce. And I didn't falsely advertize anything. Take care.
yingyinNormal.zh: 许可证，商品申报凭证，我没做虚假广告，再会。

yingyinNormal.en: From our humble beginnings, and throughout the past 15 years, Alibaba has changed commerce in China.
yingyinNormal.zh: 从我们最初很单纯的一个小期望开始，如今十五年过去了，阿里巴巴已经改变了中国电子商务的模式。

yingyinNormal.en: Did you just do what I think you did? I'm simply stating my opinion about the taxation of web commerce.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你刚才说的意思是不是和我想的一样? 我只是说了我对网络商务税收的意见。

yingyinNormal.en: My contacts in Beijing tell me the minister of commerce is in a tizzy. Wants to use this as an excuse to start clenching fists.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我在北京的联系人跟我说商务部部长很激动，他想以此为借口重拳出击。

yingyinNormal.en: Gee, I don't know. How about selling food without a permit? Transporting undeclared commerce across borough lines? False advertizing.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我也不清楚，无证经营食品吗？跨区运输未申报商品？虚假广告。

yingyinNormal.en: When our nation started the interstate highway act, instead of having local commerce, we could get goods coast to coast, top to bottom.
yingyinNormal.zh: 当我们的国家开始实施了州际高速公路法案来代替当地的商业，我们可以获得商品东海岸到西海岸从上到下。

yingyinNormal.en: Our delegation to the Joint Commission on Commerce and Trade was unfairly accused and defamed by representatives of the United States government.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们派往商贸联合委员会的代表遭到了美国政府代表的不公平指控与污蔑。

yingyinNormal.en: And its tallest is the International Commerce Center. You can take the shard and put Nelson's column on top three times and it will still be smaller.
yingyinNormal.zh: 香港最高的建筑是环球贸易广场。往夏德大厦上垒上3座纳尔逊纪念碑仍然不及它高。

yingyinNormal.en: Alright, Internet is amazing. Before I came here, searching on the Alibaba Internet, the e-commerce site, we found a stamp which is (in)1948, Hannover Messe Export.
yingyinNormal.zh: 互联网很奇妙，在我来这里之前，我在阿里巴巴电子商务网上，我们找到一枚1948年汉诺威梅西出口纪念邮票。

yingyinNormal.en: I also would love to take this opportunity to present you a small innovative product which we design, because we are E-commerce company, online payment to buy things is always a big headache.
yingyinNormal.zh: 同时我想借助这个机会，演示一个阿里巴巴开发的新产品，因为我们经营的是电子商务，在线支付有时是件头疼的事。
